### User Login

This endpoint allows users to log in to the to-do application backend.

#### Request Body

- email (string, required): The email address of the user.

- password (string, required): The password of the user.


#### Response

The response is in JSON format with the following schema:

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "token": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "message": {
            "type": "string"
        }
    }
}

 ```

- token (string): The authentication token for the logged-in user.

- message (string): A message indicating the result of the login attempt.

### User Logout

This endpoint is used to log out the user from the to-do application.

#### Request Body

- No request body is required for this endpoint.


#### Response

The response for this request is a JSON object with the following schema:

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "message": {
            "type": "string"
        }
    }
}

 ```

The response contains a "message" key which is a string indicating the status of the logout operation.

### Assign Or Update Todo Category

The endpoint allows updating the category of a specific todo item.

#### Request

- Method: PATCH

- URL: `https://to-do-application-backend-development.onrender.com/todo/category/673ec4231251f465387a5e31`

- { "category": "Grocery"}


#### Response

The response is in JSON format and follows the schema below:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "message": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "todo": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "_id": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "title": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "description": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "dueDate": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "priority": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "status": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "category": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "user": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "isDeleted": {
          "type": "boolean"
        },
        "createdAt": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "updatedAt": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "__v": {
          "type": "integer"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```
